<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFC26A7DFA929AD91416B7DE" pageId="57" pageNumber="815" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC26A7DFA929AD91416B7DE" blockId="57.[1388,2598,3156,3472]" pageId="57" pageNumber="815">
Relationships are currently unresolved. Genetic data place 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC26A7DF7549AD9173BB7AF" box="[2216,2363,3200,3229]" pageId="57" pageNumber="815" rank="subSpecies" subSpecies="bellieri">race bellieri</taxonomicName>
close to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC26A7DF6459AD91426B7AF" box="[2489,2598,3200,3229]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="815" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hypsugo</taxonomicName>
aisentrauti (but see 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC26A7DF9939AFE191FB7F6" baseAuthorityName="Hill" baseAuthorityYear="1968" box="[1647,1823,3239,3268]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="815" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eisentrauti">H. eisentrauti</taxonomicName>
). Nominate 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFC26A7DF8309AFE163DB7F6" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[1996,2109,3239,3268]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="815" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="crassulus">crassulus</taxonomicName>
has not yet been included in a phylogenetic analysis; bellieri might represent a distinct species. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
